lead_paragraph: Inter Milan's Serie A title hopes suffered a setback as they conceded a stoppage-time equaliser and were held 1-1 at home by relegation-threatened Carpi on Sunday and leaders Napoli swept to a 4-2 win at Sampdoria.

headline.print_headline: Napoli Score Four to Stay Top, Inter Held by Carpi
